### TX Server Test Requests
### Use with REST Client extension in VSCode

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/tx/r4

### ========================================
### Metadata & Capability Statement
### ========================================

### Get server metadata (CapabilityStatement)
GET {{baseUrl}}/metadata
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### ========================================
### CodeSystem Operations
### ========================================

### List all CodeSystems
GET {{baseUrl}}/CodeSystem
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### List CodeSystems (first 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/CodeSystem?_count=10
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### Search CodeSystem by URL (SNOMED CT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/CodeSystem?url=http://snomed.info/sct
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### Search CodeSystem by URL (LOINC)
GET {{baseUrl}}/CodeSystem?url=http://loinc.org
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### Lookup a SNOMED CT code (e.g., 73211009 = Diabetes mellitus)
GET {{baseUrl}}/CodeSystem/$lookup?system=http://snomed.info/sct&code=73211009
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### Lookup a SNOMED CT code with display (e.g., 22298006 = Myocardial infarction)
GET {{baseUrl}}/CodeSystem/$lookup?system=http://snomed.info/sct&code=22298006
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### Lookup LOINC code (e.g., 8867-4 = Heart rate)
GET {{baseUrl}}/CodeSystem/$lookup?system=http://loinc.org&code=8867-4
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### Validate SNOMED code
GET {{baseUrl}}/CodeSystem/$validate-code?url=http://snomed.info/sct&code=73211009
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### ========================================
### ValueSet Operations
### ========================================

### List all ValueSets
GET {{baseUrl}}/ValueSet
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### List ValueSets (first 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/ValueSet?_count=10
Accept: application/fhir+json

###

### Expand a ValueSet by URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/ValueSet/$expand
Content-Type: application/fhir+json
Accept: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Parameters",
  "parameter": [
    {
      "name": "url",
      "valueUri": "http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/languages"
    },
    {
      "name": "count",
      "valueInteger": 20
    }
  ]
}

###

### Validate code against ValueSet
POST {{baseUrl}}/ValueSet/$validate-code
Content-Type: application/fhir+json
Accept: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Parameters",
  "parameter": [
    {
      "name": "url",
      "valueUri": "http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/languages"
    },
    {
      "name": "code",
      "valueCode": "en"
    },
    {
      "name": "system",
      "valueUri": "urn:ietf:bcp:47"
    }
  ]
}

###

### ========================================
### Health Check
### ========================================

### Server health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Root endpoint
GET http://localhost:3000/
Accept: application/json
